[0.022, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m   LP-0008 — autonomous AI agent on Logos\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   a step-by-step walkthrough of every success criterion\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   real zero-knowledge proofs · RISC0_DEV_MODE=0\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.073, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 1 · Loads into Logos Core, beside the platform modules\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F1 — loads alongside wallet/storage/messaging, no changes to them\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.208, "o", "\u001b[1m$ RISC0_DEV_MODE=0 sequencer_service   # the LEZ chain\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.646, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  block 1427\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.543, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  block 1428\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.521, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m$ RISC0_DEV_MODE=0 logoscore -D   # the agent daemon\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.352, "o", "  loaded capability_module\r\n  loaded storage_module\r\n  loaded lez_wallet_module\r\n  loaded chat_module\r\n  loaded delivery_module\r\n  loaded agent_module\r\n"]
[0.086, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m   ✓ 6 modules, 0 crashed — agent runs next to the platform modules\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.010, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 2 · One command to deploy + configure on any node\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F3 — single CLI command deploys the agent headless\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[3.205, "o", "\u001b[1m$ agent up   # deploy + load + configure, one command\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.609, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  spawns logoscore -D, loads the modules, sets the owner + limits\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.507, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  (the boot you just saw, wrapped into one command — agent-cli/)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.508, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Single-command deploy on any machine running Logos Core headless.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.007, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 3 · It owns a shielded LEZ account\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m   criterion: F2 — own shielded account, sends + receives independently of the owner\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.206, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call lez_wallet_module balance\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.685, "o", "  {\"method\":\"balance\",\"module\":\"lez_wallet_module\",\"result\":\"75\",\"status\":\"ok\"}\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call agent_module meta_status   # balance + active tasks\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.678, "o", "  balance: 75 · active tasks: 34\r\n"]
[0.006, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Its own funds and task state. Spends them itself, not the owner's wallet.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.010, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 4 · All default skills, behind an extensible interface\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F6 + U1 — all skills implemented; 3rd parties can add more\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.208, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call agent_module meta_skills\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.668, "o", "  21 skills:\r\n    storage.upload, storage.download, storage.list, storage.share, messaging.send, messaging.join, messaging.create_group, wallet.balance, wallet.send, wallet.history, program.query\r\n    program.call, program.deploy, agent.card, agent.discover, agent.task, agent.subscribe, agent.cancel, meta.skills, meta.status, meta.configure\r\n"]
[0.005, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Storage, messaging, blockchain, A2A, meta — all present. Add skills via docs/SKILL_INTERFACE.md.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.006, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 5 · A2A-compatible identity card\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F7 — Agent Card follows the A2A schema (+ Logos payment/transport)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.209, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call agent_module agent_card | jq\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.658, "o", "  {\r\n    \"name\": \"LP-0008 Autonomous Agent\",\r\n    \"capabilities\": {\r\n      \"extendedAgentCard\": true,\r\n      \"pushNotifications\": false,\r\n      \"streaming\": false\r\n    },\r\n    \"x-lez-identity\": \"<shielded keys>\"\r\n  }\r\n"]
[0.004, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m   ✓ A2A schema + x-lez extension (shielded keys). Transport binding in docs/A2A_BINDING.md.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.008, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;36m▌ 6 · Owner reaches the agent over encrypted messaging\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F4 — owner interacts from a separate app instance, no server\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.209, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call agent_module messaging_send <owner channel>\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.663, "o", "  {\"method\":\"messaging_send\",\"module\":\"agent_module\",\"result\":\"{\\\"result\\\":{\\\"convo_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"recipient\\\":\\\"owner-channel\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"sent\\\"}}\",\"status\":\"ok\"}\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Dedicated encrypted owner channel. No server, no exposed API.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.011, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 7 · USE CASE 1 — a real on-chain payment\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m   criterion: F (on-chain action) + P1 — CU cost documented, real proof\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.269, "o", "\u001b[1m$ RISC0_DEV_MODE=0 wallet auth-transfer send --amount 7   # watch the prover\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.683, "o", "  131072 total cycles\r\n  77975 user cycles (59.49%)\r\n"]
[17.717, "o", "  262144 total cycles\r\n  184479 user cycles (70.37%)\r\n"]
[86.642, "o", "  tx: 423fe9e21d2c5255b6f02146b9bc08a19d024e8bfd24d9ee4a27f5241f0bd8d7\r\n"]
[9.456, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  recipient: 0 → 7\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.508, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Private transfer settled on-chain. 393,216 guest cycles — full CU table in docs/CU_COSTS.md.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.009, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 8 · Spending limits — autonomous below, approval above\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F5 + R2 — threshold gate; above-limit held; if owner unreachable, not executed\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.212, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  policy: per-transaction limit = 50 LEZ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.511, "o", "\u001b[1m$ agent_task at price 80  (over the 50 limit) — should be held\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.867, "o", "  amount 80 LEZ · status: pending_approval\r\n  reason: spend exceeds autonomous threshold\r\n"]
[0.004, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  → NOT executed. Owner unreachable → retries, then reports.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.508, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Above the limit, the spend is held for the owner. Never auto-sent (R2).\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.006, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 9 · USE CASE 2 — a private file vault\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m   criterion: F9 — store + retrieve end-to-end\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[6.368, "o", "\u001b[1m$ storage: uploadInit → uploadChunk → uploadFinalize → CID\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.129, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  CID  zDvZRwzkyy2RfSZiwxjvqUBP4E5u9urXaUnMu34WdKG8qt8vk9vN\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.615, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  exists: true    download: ok\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.508, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Encrypt → store → content address → retrieve. No cloud provider.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.010, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;36m▌ 10 · Survives a restart without losing task state\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: R1 — recovers from node restart, pending work preserved\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.267, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  pending task records on disk: 52\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.509, "o", "\u001b[1m$ kill the daemon, then restart it\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.655, "o", "tests/demo-full-a.sh: line 117: 22447 Killed: 9               RISC0_DEV_MODE=0 nohup \"$LC\" -D -m \"$M\" > \"$DLOG\" 2>&1\r\n"]
[3.009, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  daemon killed.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.931, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  after restart, task records still on disk: 52\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.509, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Task state persisted across the restart — nothing lost.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.008, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 11 · A failing skill does not crash the module\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: R3 — skill failures are isolated\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.209, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call agent_module storage_download <bad-cid>   # made to fail\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.675, "o", "  skill returned: error (isolated)\r\n"]
[0.059, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  module still loaded: yes\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.508, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m   ✓ The skill failed, the module kept running. Failures don't cascade.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.010, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 12 · Deployed on the hosted testnet\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F10 + S1 — 3 agents, one per skill category, on testnet\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[3.210, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  Storage agent      — funded, addressable\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.513, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  Messaging agent    — funded, addressable\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.511, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  Blockchain agent   — funded; sent + received with real proofs\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.510, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Three deployed agents, reproduce steps + tx hashes in docs/TESTNET_EVIDENCE.md.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.011, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 13 · Everything else, in the repo\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F11 · U2 · S2 · S3 · S4 — docs, Basecamp app, CI, README\u001b[0m\r\n"]
